sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as User / Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InlineEval as RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>(in-process)
    participant DatasetIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Ragas as Ragas evaluate()<br/>(in-process)
    participant InlineLLM as LlamaStackInlineLLM<br/>(wrapper)
    participant InlineEmbed as LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings<br/>(wrapper)
    participant Inference as Ollama / vLLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,Inference: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LLS->>InlineEval: Delegate eval (in-process)
    InlineEval->>DatasetIO: iterrows() - retrieve dataset<br/>(in-process Python call)
    DatasetIO-->>InlineEval: EvaluationDataset rows
    InlineEval->>Ragas: evaluate(dataset, metrics)<br/>(in-process Python call)

    loop For each metric evaluation
        Ragas->>InlineLLM: generate_text(prompt)<br/>(BaseRagasLLM interface)
        InlineLLM->>LLS: openai_completion()<br/>(in-process API)
        LLS->>Inference: LLM completion<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Inference-->>LLS: Completion result
        LLS-->>InlineLLM: LLMResult
        InlineLLM-->>Ragas: LLMResult / Generation

        Ragas->>InlineEmbed: embed_text(texts)<br/>(BaseRagasEmbeddings interface)
        InlineEmbed->>LLS: openai_embeddings()<br/>(in-process API)
        LLS->>Inference: Embedding request<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Inference-->>LLS: Embedding vectors
        LLS-->>InlineEmbed: Embeddings
        InlineEmbed-->>Ragas: List[float]
    end

    Ragas-->>InlineEval: EvaluationResult (scores)
    InlineEval-->>LLS: Job result stored (in-memory)
    LLS-->>Client: Job ID

    Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job_result
    LLS-->>Client: Evaluation scores (JSON)

    Note over Client,Inference: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    participant RemoteEval as RagasEvaluatorRemote
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPData as KFP: retrieve_data<br/>(pipeline step 1)
    participant KFPRagas as KFP: run_ragas_eval<br/>(pipeline step 2)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LLS->>RemoteEval: Delegate eval
    RemoteEval->>K8sAPI: Read ConfigMap<br/>trustyai-service-operator-config<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>RemoteEval: Base image URL
    RemoteEval->>RemoteEval: Compile KFP pipeline YAML
    RemoteEval->>KFP: create_run(pipeline)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token (OAuth)
    KFP-->>RemoteEval: Run ID
    RemoteEval-->>LLS: Job ID (stored in-memory)
    LLS-->>Client: Job ID

    KFP->>KFPData: Execute step 1
    KFPData->>LLS: GET dataset rows<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LLS-->>KFPData: Dataset rows
    KFPData->>KFPRagas: Pass dataset

    loop For each metric evaluation
        KFPRagas->>LLS: LLM completion<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LLS->>Inference: Forward to backend<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Inference-->>LLS: Result
        LLS-->>KFPRagas: Completion

        KFPRagas->>LLS: Embedding request<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LLS->>Inference: Forward to backend<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Inference-->>LLS: Vectors
        LLS-->>KFPRagas: Embeddings
    end

    KFPRagas->>S3: PUT results JSONL<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM
    KFPRagas-->>KFP: Step complete

    Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job_status
    LLS->>RemoteEval: Check status
    RemoteEval->>KFP: get_run(run_id)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
    KFP-->>RemoteEval: Run status
    RemoteEval-->>LLS: Job status
    LLS-->>Client: Status (completed)

    Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job_result
    LLS->>RemoteEval: Get results
    RemoteEval->>S3: GET results JSONL<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM
    S3-->>RemoteEval: Evaluation results
    RemoteEval-->>LLS: Parsed results
    LLS-->>Client: Evaluation scores (JSON)
